      | Target entity              | Customer User          |
      | Related entity data fields | ID                     |
      | Related entity info title  | [First Name,Last Name] |
      | Related entity detailed    | [First Name,Last Name] |
      | Searchable                 | Yes                    |
      | Filterable                 | Yes                    |
